_sText:
Fy_corner by goombus

Map type: Fight Yard
Number of players: 24

Update* Now with newly updated painted nav file from Chizbone! Giving you the edge of fun! 

Credits to Chizbone for Nav file

Very simple map with simple gameplay.

Just get round that corner and kill!

This is mainly designed towards Deathmatch servers.
But still fun for normal quick rounds.
(It could also help you train for corner encounters ^^)

Have fun!

Place the bsp. and nav. file into this directory.

C:\Program Files\Steam\steamapps\(username)\counter-strike source\cstrike\maps

p.s I have to be honest, this was only 10 minutes work. It's VERY simple... Didn't have much time on my hands, so I made something quick.
